abstract: Can you help us identify any of the fans who were there to see Alex Rodriguez leave after striking out in the last game of the Yankees' season?
snippet: Can you help us identify any of the fans who were there to see Alex Rodriguez leave after striking out in the last game of the Yankees' season?
lead_paragraph: Alex Rodriguez exited stage right Thursday night after striking out to end the Yankees' season far sooner than many fans had hoped. Can you help us identify any of the fans in this photo who were there to see him off? E-mail us at nytsportsphoto@gmail.com.
